a articleid=\"554400000181476\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part I, Subpart i, Chapter 2, Section B - A Representative’s Right to Notification and Review of Records\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000181476/M21-1-Part-I-Subpart-i-Chapter-2-Section-B-A-Representatives-Right-to-Notification-and-Review-of-Records\">M21-1, Part I, Subpart i, 2.B.1.c and d</a>, and</span></span></div></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">electronic notification, see the <a href=\"https://vbaw.vba.va.gov/PRODUCTIONOFFICE/vbms-job-aids-demos.asp\" target=\"_blank\"><i>POA Electronic Notification Fact Sheet</i></a>.</span></span></div></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"><h3><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\">V.iv.1.D.2.c<a id=\"2c\" name=\"2c\">.</a>  Preparing Rating Decisions for Other Entities</span></span></span></span></span></span></h3></td><td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\"> </span></span></p></td><td style=\"width: 516px; padding: 0px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Use the table below to find relevant references for preparing rating decisions for other entities.</span></span></div><div></div><div><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"border-spacing: 1px; border-collapse: revert;\" summary=\"This is an if-then table.  Column 1 contains the criteria and column 2 contains the relevant procedures to follow.\" width=\"626\"><thead><tr><th style=\"padding: 1px;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><b>If ...</b></span></span></div></th><th style=\"padding: 1px;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><b>Then follow the relevant procedures in ...</b></span></span></div></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding: 1px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">rating action is <i>specifically</i> requested by the Department of Veterans Affairs Insurance Center in Philadelphia</span></span></div></td><td style=\"padding: 1px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a articleid=\"554400000177980\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part X, Subpart ii, Chapter 6, Section G - Competency Determinations for the Insurance Center (IC)\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000177980/M21-1-Part-X-Subpart-ii-Chapter-6-Section-G-Competency-Determinations-for-the-Insurance-Center-IC\">M21-1, Part X, Subpart ii, 6.G.1.g</a> for insurance purposes.</span></span></div></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 1px;\"><ul><li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">the Veteran is an active recipient of benefits under <a href=\"https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/38/part-III/chapter-31\">Chapter 31</a>, and</span></span></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">the rating decision effectuates one of the following outcomes:</span></span></div><ul><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">implements a final determination of service connection (SC) when only a memorandum rating decision for vocational rehabilitation purposes is otherwise of record</span></span></div></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">awards entitlement to individual unemployability benefits</span></span></div></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">reduces the evaluation of a service-connected disability, or</span></span></div></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">severs SC</span></span></div></li></ul></li></ul></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 1px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a articleid=\"554400000173834\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part XIII, Subpart i, Chapter 5, Section B - Memorandum Vocational Rehabilitation/Employment (VR&amp;E) Ratings\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000173834/M21-1-Part-XIII-Subpart-i-Chapter-5-Section-B-Memorandum-Vocational-RehabilitationEmployment-VRE-Ratings\">M21-1, Part XIII, Subpart i, 5.B.3.g</a> to ensure Veteran Readiness and Employment Service is provided notice of a rating decision.</span></span></div></td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 1px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">the Veterans Health Administration <i>requests</i> a determination of SC for treatment purposes</span></span></div></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 1px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a articleid=\"554400000173640\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part XIII, Subpart i, Chapter 3, Section A - General Information on Eligibility for Medical Services\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000173640/M21-1-Part-XIII-Subpart-i-Chapter-3-Section-A-General-Information-on-Eligibility-for-Medical-Services\">M21-1, Part XIII, Subpart i, 3.A.4.c</a> to take the appropriate rating action.</span></span></div></td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 1px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">preparing a rating decision that affects a beneficiary’s competency status</span></span></div></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 1px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a articleid=\"554400000177974\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part X, Subpart ii, Chapter 6, Section A - Evaluating and Rating Competency\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000177974/M21-1-Part-X-Subpart-ii-Chapter-6-Section-A-Evaluating-and-Rating-Competency\">M21-1, Part X, Subpart ii, 6</a>.</span></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> </span></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><p class=\"ng-scope\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\"><a href=\"#top\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px\">To Top</span></a>